	Creating Suggestions
</p>

<p>
	Creating suggestions is very simple. Click on Suggestions on the navigation bar at the top of the screen. On the bottom of the suggestion list
	is a green button for new suggestions. All a suggestion requires is that you provide a meaningful title and a detailed description. Once you save
	your suggestion you can edit it again later.
</p>

